<odoo>
  <record id="ir_ui_view_3840" model="ir.ui.view">
    <field name="arch" type="xml">
      <data name="Appointment Types" track="1" inherit_id="website_appointment.appointments_cards_layout">
        <xpath expr="//div[hasclass('oe_empty')]" position="replace">
          <div class="oe_structure oe_empty">
            <section class="s_text_image pb80 o_colored_level pt16" data-snippet="s_text_image" data-name="Text - Image">
              <div class="container">
                <div class="row o_grid_mode" data-row-count="11">
                  <div class="o_colored_level o_grid_item g-col-lg-7 g-height-11 col-lg-7" style="grid-area: 1 / 1 / 12 / 8; z-index: 1;">
                    <h2 class="h3-fs">Discover Belgium’s Most Captivating Cities with a Local Guide</h2>
                    <div>
                      <br/>
                    </div>
                    <p>Embark on an unforgettable journey through four of Belgium’s most iconic cities — <strong>Brussels, Antwerp, Ghent, and Namur</strong> — each offering a unique blend of history, culture, and charm.</p>
                    <ul>
                      <li>
                        <p><strong>Brussels</strong>, the heart of Europe, welcomes you with grand architecture, cobblestone streets, and a vibrant atmosphere. From the opulent Grand Place to the surreal world of Magritte, this city is a must-see for culture lovers and history buffs alike.</p>
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        <p><strong>Antwerp</strong> dazzles with its fashion-forward spirit and rich artistic heritage. Explore the legacy of Rubens, marvel at the gothic Cathedral of Our Lady, and stroll through the dynamic streets of this port city where tradition meets modern creativity.</p>
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        <p><strong>Ghent</strong> enchants with medieval splendor and a youthful energy. Discover castles, canals, and hidden alleyways as you uncover the soul of a city where past and present coexist in perfect harmony.</p>
                      </li>
                      <li>
                        <p><strong>Namur</strong>, nestled at the confluence of the Meuse and Sambre rivers, invites you to slow down and savor the beauty of Wallonia. Its imposing citadel, relaxed charm, and panoramic views make it a serene yet fascinating stop on your Belgian adventure.</p>
                      </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>Whether you're a first-time visitor or rediscovering Belgium, our guided tours offer insider stories, hidden gems, and unforgettable moments.</p>
                  </div>
                  <div class="o_colored_level o_grid_item o_grid_item_image g-height-11 col-lg-4 g-col-lg-4" style="z-index: 2; grid-area: 1 / 9 / 12 / 13;">
                    <img src="/web/image/guided_tours.ir_attachment_7" alt="" class="img img-fluid mx-auto rounded o_we_custom_image"  data-resize-width="690" data-mimetype="image/webp"/>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>
          </div>
        </xpath>
      </data>
    </field>
